</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n連721都唔會4個部門一齊見記者，點解831會？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我依家信太子有無辜市民被殺害了</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一句到尾啦，係支共命令&quot;止暴制亂&quot;之下，明知一日拖一日尤其頭七都唔交出足本只會愈拖愈亂，咁都唔交你地話點解呢？？？？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加埋依家毛EE爆料，831事件冇人死？？？<br />\n<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFYI，當晚現場傳第一消息：有人打死人，但唔係香港警察，你話係邊個呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？！！！</span></span></span></strong></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5a65d712f99e3bf324acfe2fd14452f4daa940be","tid":1563261,"uid":283712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:03:51.000Z","msg":"朱同學，你唔使講對唔住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24de5879a0672579886b1590dd90e8a70eac604b","tid":1563261,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:10:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f534ac0a9bba43dc087d8e166ae7bbaa34242729","tid":1563261,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"屌那星下下扑後腦唔死都癱<br />\n班黑警真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"bd77bc0e78db1cca0b8e8df33f6e75b864071421","tid":1563261,"uid":268160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"T